<div class="dummyContent">
<p>本文档由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sanks269" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3671347); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3671347&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160549" alt="sanks269" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3671347)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sanks269" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3671347); return false;">sanks269</a></span>与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/solvex" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2419995); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2419995&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160549" alt="solvex" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2419995)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/solvex" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2419995); return false;">solvex</a></span>合著。<br />
本文档同时参加<a href="http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/usocontest2020-hub">2020谎言竞赛</a>。</p>
